OL,3,CGwent Police Chief condemns 'utterly
OL,4,Cvile' messages from former officers
OL,6,FThe Chief Constable of Gwent Police
OL,7,Fhas condemned what he described as
OL,8,F"utterly vile and shocking" WhatsApp
OL,9,Fmessages shared by two former police
OL,10,Fconstables.
OL,12,FSimon Lewis and James Heley resigned
OL,13,Fon Friday, 27 February, ahead of a
OL,14,Fgross misconduct hearing on Monday, 2
OL,15,FMarch.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/6
