OL,3,CGwent Police Chief condemns 'utterly
OL,4,Cvile' messages from former officers
OL,6,FThe hearing panel ruled that both
OL,7,Fofficers, who shared racist,
OL,8,Fhomophobic, and misogynistic messages
OL,9,Fwithin a private WhatsApp group, would
OL,10,Fhave been dismissed without notice had
OL,11,Fthey not already resigned.
OL,13,FBoth former PCs Lewis and Heley were
OL,14,Ffound to have breached the Standards
OL,15,Fof Professional Behaviour.
OL,16,FAdditionally, Heley was found to have
OL,17,Fbreached standards regarding
OL,18,Fconfidentiality.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
