CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1772565071
OL,3,CGwent Police Chief condemns 'utterly
OL,4,Cvile' messages from former officers
OL,6,FThe allegations related to messages
OL,7,Fsent between April 2015 and February
OL,8,F2019.
OL,10,FFollowing the hearing, Chief Constable
OL,11,FMark Hobrough said: "The WhatsApp
OL,12,Fmessages sent by these former officers
OL,13,Fwere utterly vile and shocking,
OL,14,Fshowing blatant racism, homophobia,
OL,15,Fand misogyny, attitudes that have
OL,16,Fabsolutely no place in policing or our
OL,17,Fsociety.
OL,26,@sD@UOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/6
