PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1772565071
OL,3,CGwent Police Chief condemns 'utterly
OL,4,Cvile' messages from former officers
OL,6,F"It is right that both former PCs
OL,7,FSimon Lewis and James Heley are no
OL,8,Flonger part of Gwent Police. Their
OL,9,Factions have brought shame to our
OL,10,Forganisation and have undermined
OL,11,Fpublic trust."
OL,13,F"We acted swiftly the moment we were
OL,14,Fmade aware of these messages in 2022,
OL,15,Fwhich included the immediate
OL,16,Fsuspension of these two officers and
OL,17,Freferrals to the Independent Office
OL,18,Ffor Police Conduct (IOPC).
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
