PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1772565071
OL,3,CGwent Police Chief condemns 'utterly
OL,4,Cvile' messages from former officers
OL,6,F"In recent years, we have made
OL,7,Fsignificant progress in rooting out
OL,8,Fmisconduct and driving substantial
OL,9,Fcultural change. My mission is to
OL,10,Frestore trust with our communities by
OL,11,Fbuilding an inclusive organisation
OL,12,Fthat genuinely cares for and engages
OL,13,Fwith everyone.
OL,15,F"The vast majority of our officers
OL,16,Fserve with pride, professionalism, and
OL,17,Fintegrity. Our communities, and our
OL,18,Fstaff, deserve nothing less than the
OL,19,Fhighest standards."
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU{D@SO]
