OL,3,CGwent Police Chief condemns 'utterly
OL,4,Cvile' messages from former officers
OL,6,FBoth former officers will now be
OL,7,Fplaced on the College of Policing's
OL,8,Fbarred list, preventing them from
OL,9,Fserving in law enforcement again.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/6
